game,  some  risk  capital,  and  it’s  not  just  the  public  sector  putting 
up  the  dough  and  the  private  sector  reaping  the  benefits  at  the 
back  end  of  the  project.  So  if  at  some  point  you  could  comment  on 
that as well. 

But Mr. Chairman, thank you for letting me, as a member of the 
Senate,  have  a  chance  to  make  a  couple  comments.  And  again,  I 
look forward to working with you on this and very other important 
matters on this committee. 

