state like Illinois, where it is very rural once you get south of Inter-
state 80. Broadband is very important. 

As  we  build  roads  into  rural  parts  of  states  like  Illinois,  Min-
nesota,  or  Virginia,  we  need  to  figure  out  ways  to  make  sure  that 
people have access to the world. I think that’s what we really ought 
to be thinking about in the reauthorization. 

Senator KLOBUCHAR. Thank you very much. 
Mr. LAHOOD. Thank you. 
