Mr. LAHOOD. Thank you. 
Senator MCCASKILL. Thank you, Mr. Chairman. 
The CHAIRMAN. Thank you, Senator. Senator Warner? 
Senator  WARNER.  Thank  you,  Mr.  Chairman.  I  want  to  go  back 
to  the  three  points  that  I’d  raised  earlier,  Representative  LaHood. 
And first of all let me acknowledge this first question is more—you 
haven’t gotten there yet, you’ve got your arms around a very, very 
large department—but again, my prior experience as Governor and 
